333
00:23:40,910 --> 00:23:41,960
Or maybe,

334
00:23:42,390 --> 00:23:44,080
he forgot our promise.

335
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:47,200
After all, I’m not Liuying.

336
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:48,680
I’m just Ayu

337
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:50,440
