338
00:23:51,360 --> 00:23:52,230
It’s not true.

339
00:23:52,390 --> 00:23:53,600
Stop guessing.

340
00:23:58,270 --> 00:24:00,360
What’s wrong with the Dragon King?

341
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:05,750
