410
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:27,960
Trust me.

411
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,630
Your dream will come true soon.

412
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,600
Consort Dowager Yu, look,

413
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:57,320
